### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "country": "Ghana",
  "full_name": "Dev User",
  "username": "devuser",
  "email": "devuser@yenkasa.com",
  "phone_number": "+233241234567",
  "signup_type": "developer",
  "password": "StrongPass123!",
  "agree_to_terms": true
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "devuser@yenkasa.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

### Repository ingestion
POST http://localhost:8080/api/repo/ingestions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_path": "/workspace/samples/repositories/dev_intelligence_sample",
  "repo_name": "dev-intelligence-sample",
  "force_reingest": true
}

### Repository search
GET http://localhost:8080/api/repo/search?q=Where%20is%20wallet%20balance%20handled%3F&repo_name=dev-intelligence-sample
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Repository chat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/repo/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_name": "dev-intelligence-sample",
  "question": "Explain how wallet balance retrieval and notifications are split across this repository."
}
